Package: pcgamedeals
Type: Package
Title: PC Game Deal Information 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors: Neethu Gopalakrishna, Disha Divakar Holla and Kristy Phipps
Maintainer: Kristy Phipps <phipps.kristy@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows for easy direct querying of the Deal Shark API. 
    There are 4 main functions that return information to the user as a dataframe for further personal exploration. 
    There is a main function that requests user input and will deliver a fully realized response based on users responses. 
